## 2026-04-04 - Inconsistent async cleanup across UI hooks
- Added `signal.aborted` guards before every `setState` call in async paths across four hooks:
  - `useGenerators.ts`: added `if (controller.signal.aborted) return;` before `setGenerators(data)` in try block; changed `setLoading(false)` in finally to `if (!controller.signal.aborted) setLoading(false);`
